description:
Collects Engineer (2007 Arcana Studio) #1-2, plus #3 (previously unreleased). Written by Brian Churilla and Jeremy Shepherd. Art by Brian Churilla. An ancient sentient entity is feasting on the very fabric of space and time. Only one man can stop it: The Engineer, last survivor of the destroyed Earth. Utilizing a colossal pipe organ that enables pan-dimensional travel, The Engineer pursues the lost components of The Konstrukt, an archaic mechanism that imbues whoever possesses it with the ability to manipulate reality itself, in the hopes of using it to defeat the creature and undo the incalculable damage it has already done. Collects and completes The Engineer series. Hardcover, 138 pages, full color. Cover price $9.95.

Hardcover collecting Engineer: Konstrukt.
name: Engineer: Konstrukt
